
Time Flight Sensor:

Vin to Pin 1 (3.3V)
GND to Pin 6 (GND)
SDA to Pin 3 (GPIO 2)
SCL to Pin 5 (GPIO 3)

Accelerometer:

VCC to Pin 1 (3.3 V)
GND to Pin 6 (GND)
SCL to Pin 5 (GPIO 3)
SDA to Pin 3 (GPIO 2)

RGB Color Sensor:

VCC (both) to Pin 1 (3.3V)
GND (both) to Pin 9 (GND)
S0 to Pin 11 (GPIO 17)
S1 to Pin 13 (GPIO 27)
S2 to Pin 15 (GPIO 22)
S3 to Pin 16 (GPIO 23)
OUT to Pin 18 (GPIO 24)
LED to Pin 22 (GPIO 25)
